The evidence with the title 'Fraud statistics ' says Conservatively, fraud steals $80 billion a year across all lines of insurance.  ... Fraud accounts for 5 - 10 percent of claims costs for U.S. and Canadian insurers.  ... More than half ( 56 percent) paid cash for their last home repair or improvement .  ... The average two - car family in Florida pays nearly $ 100 more in auto premiums ... 
